.000Z","msg":"不如辭職驗證一下係咪office嘅問題先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T16:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T17:08:57.000Z","msg":"Keyboard 唔好離身太遠。身體唔好向前傾，唔好Dup低個頭睇Mon。<br />\n<br />\n講就易，真係做野時根本唔會記得咩正確姿勢，同埋緊張好易會縮膊，令頸肩緊。<br />\n返工時最好每個鐘Break一次，拉一拉根，但其實作用不大，只係好少少。<br />\n比人按都係無咩用，只係好短時間有效。<br />\n最好解決方法係做Yoga，花少少時間拉番鬆緊張肌肉就會好好多。長遠個人姿勢都會有改善。"},{"pid":"c1b6d4953b4fa16248e781b1c51caa7953635c97","tid":816274,"uid":115383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad4cb921245f18450446b54420e25527cf2367db","tid":816274,"uid":72093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c95e66210dfd20c16ca17116bd2a2fd44e11993","tid":816274,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:50:41.000Z","msg":"不如辭職驗證一下係咪office嘅問題先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T16:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T01:06:17.000Z","msg":"持本書夾係腋下"},{"pid":"3301a39852f2741500bd83e4d82bae7dee56ec0f","tid":816274,"uid":115383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1b6d4953b4fa16248e781b1c51caa7953635c97","tid":816274,"uid":115383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad4cb921245f18450446b54420e25527cf2367db","tid":816274,"uid":72093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c95e66210dfd20c16ca17116bd2a2fd44e11993","tid":816274,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:50:41.000Z","msg":"不如辭職驗證一下係咪office嘅問題先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T16:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T01:06:17.000Z","msg":"持本書夾係腋下"},"cite